list.query: SELECT value, testName FROM testStartEnd WHERE type = 'started' GROUP BY runId LIMIT 1

targets.expr:
sum(
  avg_over_time(jmeter_request_size_in_bytes_sum{requestName=~".+XX.+", requestDirection="sent"}[${__range_s}s])
  / avg_over_time(jmeter_request_size_in_bytes_count{requestName=~".+XX.+", requestDirection="sent"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName)
* sum(
  irate(jmeter_requests{requestName=~".+XX.+"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName)

sum(
  avg_over_time(jmeter_request_size_in_bytes_sum{requestName=~".+XX.+", requestDirection="received"}[${__range_s}s])
  / avg_over_time(jmeter_request_size_in_bytes_count{requestName=~".+XX.+", requestDirection="received"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName)
* sum(
  irate(jmeter_requests{requestName=~".+XX.+"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName)

sum(
max_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName=~".+XX.+", requestStatus="FAIL"}[${__range_s}s])
- min_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName=~".+XX.+", requestStatus="FAIL"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName)
/ sum(
max_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName=~".+XX.+"}[${__range_s}s])
- min_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName=~".+XX.+"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName)

sum(
max_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName!~".+XX.+", requestStatus="FAIL"}[${__range_s}s])
- min_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName!~".+XX.+", requestStatus="FAIL"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, responseCode, responseMessage)

sum(
max_over_time(requests_latency_secondsHistogram_count{group="$GatlingTransaction", responseCode!="0", error!=""}[${__range_s}s]) 
- min_over_time(requests_latency_secondsHistogram_count{group="$GatlingTransaction", responseCode!="0", error!=""}[${__range_s}s])
) by (metric, error, responseCode)

sum(
max_over_time(requests_latency_secondsHistogram_count{group="$GatlingTransaction", oK="KO"}[${__range_s}s])
- min_over_time(requests_latency_secondsHistogram_count{group="$GatlingTransaction", oK="KO"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (metric)
/ sum(
max_over_time(requests_latency_secondsHistogram_count{group="$GatlingTransaction"}[${__range_s}s])
- min_over_time(requests_latency_secondsHistogram_count{group="$GatlingTransaction"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (metric)
